high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the counter, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the large metal knife off of the counter.
Walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the large metal knife in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean knife.
Walk over to the white table that is against the wall behind you.
Put the clean knife on the dirty plate that is closest to the brown cup on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean metal knife on a plate on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink that is on your right
Pick up the knife that is behind the sink next to the salt shaker
Take a step to your right and continue to stand in front of the sink
Place the knife into the sink and turn on the water to rinse the knife.  Turn off the water and pick up the knife
Turn right and walk to the wall, then hang right and cross the room to the trash bag on the floor.  At the trash bag turn right and face the side of the white table
Place the knife on the dirty plate that is sitting on the table closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean knife on a dirty plate

high_descs: Walk to the sink to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the sharp knife from behind the faucet.
Move to the right side of the sink.
Place the knife in the sink, rinse the knife off with water, pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn around and walk towards the garbage bag on the other side of the room, and turn right to face the table.
Put the knife down on the plate that's closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off the knife and put the knife down on the plate.
